scene.message:
Yukino: Honestly, it'll be{nl}
sundown soon. When are we{nl}
ever getting to the hospital?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Nurse Natsumi's got{nl}
that sexy, grown-up vibe{nl}
going on, huh!{waitkey}{ret}

Student: But even if she{nl}
can't cook, you can just buy{nl}
something at the store.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Oh yeah! Then from{nl}
now on, why not have Nurse{nl}
Natsumi make your lunch?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Come to think of it,{nl}
Nurse Natsumi broke up with{nl}
her guy! Wonder why?{waitkey}{ret}
